qDef.qDef:
Pick($(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
,
	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},Year={$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
	-Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},Year={$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
,
	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},Year={$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
	-Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},Year={$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
)/1000
